name: _timeVoid
description:
The year is 2436. Humanity has been going through a technological renaissance. Scientific breakthroughs are frequent, and feats that seemed impossible even as little as 5 years ago, have been made a reality. Concepts such as teleportation and high-speed space travel have revolutionised the world and allowed humanity to expand far beyond the reaches of Earth. Not all of these developments are good developments, however, as a newly launched project has caused problems of nightmarish proportions for the world.  You are the only one who can stop this.
